Day 16: The Power of One Sprint Goal!
🏁 "One clear goal = one powerful sprint!"  
👉 Tip: Keep the sprint goal simple, clear, and aligned with the team’s vision. A well-defined goal keeps everyone focused.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
